@lakmefashionwk Reliance Jewels Presents Monisha Jaising at Lakmé Fashion Week in partnership with FDCI.

Monisha Jaising’s collection is inspired by a laid back yet luxuriously embellished elegance incorporating the essence of a wedding in a tropical island reflecting sunshine, beach side, poolside and resort glamour. The collection attempts to merge the MJ signature style of
‘Luxury pret’ and ‘Couture’ styled perfectly with the exquisitely crafted jewellery of Reliance jewels.
